程序包 org.cloudbus.cloudsim.container.schedulers

类 ContainerVmScheduler

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.container.schedulers.ContainerVmScheduler
直接已知子类:
ContainerVmSchedulerTimeShared
public abstract class ContainerVmScheduler
extends java.lang.Object
VmScheduler is an abstract class that represents the policy used by a VMM to share processing power among VMs running in a host.
从以下版本开始:
CloudSim Toolkit 1.0
